Now in deathrun fourm, DUST! run, jump, and knife your way through this brand new deathrun map. 14 traps designed to destroy anyone who gets in thier way. this map features:
HDR lighting
Custom Materials
High Detail
5 Diffrent Endings (2 are secrets)
14 traps
and lots more!

Trap 1: Bombs Up!!!
Trap 2: Over Charge!!!
Trap 3: Sniper is the Window!!!
Trap 4: Propane Leak
Trap 5: Random Spears!!!
Trap 6: CAR BOMB!!! BOOM!
Trap 7: Killer Palm Trees
Trap 8: Smoking Creates
Trap 9: Fans
Trap 10: Achmed the dead terrorist Meets fail box
Trap 11: Falling cars, how did they get up there?
Trap 12: Mines (self activated)
Trap 13: Raising floor, how did that happen?
Trap 14: Firing Squad, they don't have training so don't laugh at their aim!
Trap 15: Bomb, go a head try to defuse it!
Trap 16: 3 sets of 2
